      <hr><a name="skip_menu"></a><h1>600 - Subject Added Entry-Personal Name (R)</h1>
      <hr>
      <div class="formatname">MARC 21 Bibliographic - Full</div>
      <div class="datename">October 2007</div>
      <hr>
      <table width="100%">
         <tr vAlign="top">
            <td width="45%"><strong>First Indicator</strong><br><em>Type of personal name entry element</em><br>0 - Forename <br>1 - Surname <br>3 - Family name <br><br></td>
            <td width="45%"><strong>Second Indicator</strong><br><em>Thesaurus</em><br>0 - Library of Congress Subject Headings <br>1 - LC subject headings for children's literature <br>2 - Medical Subject Headings <br>3 - National Agricultural Library subject authority file <br>4 - Source not specified <br>5 - Canadian Subject Headings <br>6 - R&eacute;pertoire de vedettes-mati&egrave;re <br>7 - Source specified in subfield $2 <br><br></td>
         </tr>
      </table>
